%% State Machine / Lifecycle Diagram (archviz-skills)
%% Use for: order lifecycle, approval workflow, course states, document status
%% Env: Mermaid stateDiagram-v2 (native). Preview-compatible.
%% Dials: Complexity 4, Density 3, Restraint 8
%% Anti-pattern: max 10 states, label transitions with verbs, start/end explicit

%%{init: {'theme': 'base', 'themeVariables': {'primaryColor': '#f5f0eb', 'primaryTextColor': '#1B365D', 'primaryBorderColor': '#a8a29e', 'lineColor': '#002FA7', 'fontSize': '13px'}}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> 草稿: 创建
    草稿 --> 审核中: 提交
    审核中 --> 通过: 审核通过
    审核中 --> 退回: 审核不通过
    退回 --> 草稿: 修改后重新提交
    通过 --> 公示: 进入公示期
    公示 --> 生效: 公示期满
    公示 --> 异议: 收到异议
    异议 --> 审核中: 复审
    生效 --> 归档: 执行完毕
    归档 --> [*]

    classDef default fill:#e8e4e0,stroke:#a8a29e,color:#1B365D
    classDef terminal fill:#d6d3d1,stroke:#78716c,color:#1B365D

